('Fly', 86, 'Fly B450 Qwerty ', 3140, 'Fly-B-450-front_2b111.jpg', 'Fly-B-450 has inherent memory of 23.4MB which may be expanded to8GB using the micro SD type memory card. Fly-B-450 is USB and EDGE enabled. The 5.8cm wide TFT type display with a screen resolution of 320 x 240 pixels offers enhanced user experience. Fly-B-450 also incorporates Optical Trackpad, Voice & Video chat on 2G, Nimbuzz, Snaptu, Operamini, Ebuddy, and Mobile Tracker facility.\r\n\r\nFly-B-450 has an inbuilt camera of 3.2 MP resolutions that enables great picture capture.MP3 polyphonic ringtones and video recording facility make the Fly-B-450 a great buy. Besides, Fly-B-450 includes Privacy Protection, Call Blacklist, Audio Player with Equalizer, 3.5 mm Audio Jack, Video record & play , Skype , and Video Caller ID offering an unmatched user experience. '),
('Fly', 87, 'Fly MC 125', 1450, 'Fly-MC-125-front_87907.jpg', 'Fly-MC-125 has a 4.6 cm wide TFT type display with a screen resolution of 128 X 160 pixels. There is a speaker phone and a card slot for expansion of memory. There are a host of special features that include Video Player, Audio Player with equalizer, Dedicated Audio Player Keys, FM with Telescopic antenna, Hindi/English support, Image viewer, Indian Calendar, and Calculator. That is not all; the fundamental features like alarm (5), Torch Light, Call Conference, Call Waiting, Speed Dial, Auto Redial, and Stopwatch are also incorporated.\r\n\r\nFly-MC-125 has an internal memory of 20KB which may be expanded to 8GB using the micro SD card slot.'),
('Fly', 88, 'Fly MV 135', 2761, 'Fly-MV-135-front_e0705.jpg', 'The Fly-MV-135 home theatre offers great user experience. This simple yet elegantly designed handset is equipped with a 2MP camera and video record facility. The audio player with equalizer is the other major highlight of the handset. The 6.1 cm, TFT type screen with a screen resolution of 240 * 320 pixels, displays colors in the range of 262K.\r\n\r\nThe Fly-MV-135 offers speaker phone and a card slot for memory expansion. The other special features include Nimbuzz, Opera mini, Snaptu, Calendar, Calculator, Alarm (5), Sound Recording, Image viewer, Slide show, World Clock, Unit convertor, Currency converter, Health, Speaker Size 30X40, and Stopwatch. If you thought that was all; there is more to the handset. Fly-MV-135 incorporates Ebook Reader, Call recording, and Call Black List. There is storage facility for 1000 SMS storage, along with preloaded Games. '),
('Fly', 89, 'Fly B410 DS', 2203, 'Fly-B-450-front_2b111.jpg', 'Fly-B410- DS is a QWERTY handset with features that will entice users from different walks of life. The Boom Speaker, video record and play and effective audio player are the major highlights of the Fly-B410- DS.\r\n\r\nFly-B410- DS also includes a 5.6 cm TFT type wide display. It also includes speaker phone and card slot for extensible memory. For the social networking enthusiast, the Fly-B410- DS includes, MSN Messenger, Facebook, Twitter, Nimbuz, Orkut, Google, My Space, Cricinfo, Video Record and Play, and Audio Player'),
('Onida', 90, 'Onida G480', 3697, 'p-e-m-onida-g480-front-1.wm.jpg', 'The Onida G480 is a world class phone of the G Series launched by Onida mobiles. With features like Bluetooth, MP3/Video Player, Expandable Memory and Camera, the G series mobile phones are filled with exciting features and are sure to bring a whole load of enthusiasm to your world.\r\n\r\nThe Onida G480 weighs just 75.7 grams and weighs just 110 mm x 47.8 mm x 13.8 mm giving you good portability and ease to carry it around anywhere. The Onida G480 supports a MicroSD memory card and has an extensible memory of up to 2 GB. The power management of the phone is handled by a 700 mAh Li-ion battery with a talk time of up to 210 minutes and a standby time of up to 240 hours.\r\n\r\nFor connectivity, the Onida G480 is equipped with Bluetooth, USB connector, WAP and GPRS.'),
