('Dell', 96, 'Dell XCD35', 10300, 'Dell-XCD35-front_68c26.jpg', 'Dell XCD35 features 3.2 Mega Pixel Color CMOS with Auto focus camera, it supports 3.5 inches TFT display capacitive Touch screen with 480 x 800 pixels resolution and many attractive features. This phone works over Android 2.2. Dell XCD35 provides expandable memory up to 16 GB and the internal memory is about 200 MB. The connectivity options in this hand set are Bluetooth with v2.1 with EDR, Class 2 transmit power, IEEE 802.11b/g compliant, Internal WLAN antenna, USB 2.0 with High Speed, Micro-USB, Micro-SD card access and also Support USB charging.\r\n\r\nDell XCD35 also facilitates users with video recording facility. The wide display helps users to enjoy the videos and picture with much clarity. The multimedia features like FM radio, Music Player supported with 3.5mm port and video player with MP4/H.264/H.263 player formats will certainly entice users. The Dell XCD35 mobile includes GPS which helps in finding the location and directions easily. The users can enjoy messaging feature as it has SMS, MMS, EMS and Emailing facility.\r\n\r\nThe dimensions of Dell XCD35 are 114mmx56mmx12.2mm and weight 120 gram.'),
('Dell', 97, 'Dell Venue + 4 GB Memory Card Free', 24855, 'Dell-Venue-front_cb2f3.jpg', 'Dell Venue runs on the Android 2.2 and it comes with stunning 4.1 inch WVGA AMOLED capacitive multi touch display with curved Corning Gorilla Glass, 1GHz processor with 800 x 480 pixels resolution. Dell Venue holds extraordinary 8 mega pixel camera with features like auto focus and 4x Digital Zoom which give excellent pictures to cherish life long with friends and close ones on the go.\r\n\r\nThe connectivity features are Sync to PC, Wi-Fi, AGPS, Bluetooth 2.1 with EDR, 3G Connectivity, and Micro-USB. Dell Venue also facilitates users with Video and Audio Record features. It includes dedicated camera key, 3.5 mm headset jack. The internal memory is 1 GB and external memory can be extended up to 32 GB. Dell Venue has Virtual Keyboard, USB Mass Storage and is powered with a 1400 mAh battery which gives decent performance.\r\n\r\nThere are many messaging options included in Dell Venue hand set like POP3, IMAP, ActiveSync, Push Email, Web mail, Microsoft Exchange, SMS, MMS, and Native IM. The browser has Web 2.0 full HTML and WAP Support. Other features are Predictive text, GMS HW Compliant with G-sensor, E-compass, and Virtual Keyboard. '),
('Dell', 98, 'Dell Venue Pro', 26905, 'Dell-Venue-Pro-front_e17e1.jpg', 'Dell Venue Pro is a Windows Phone7 handset and packs a slide out QWERTY keyboard and packs a 5 MP camera with LED Flash and auto focus. It gives users a fresh new way to meet everyday social and professional commitments in a sleek and attractive form. Dell Venue Pro equips 4.1-inch WVGA AMOLED capacitive display with curved Gorilla Glass, multi-touch display allows for easier navigation and has 512MB RAM and 8GB on-board storage.\r\n\r\nDell Venue Pro promises 720p HD video recording. Other features include Wi-Fi, Bluetooth, A-GPS, and micro USB support. The users can enjoy gaming experience on the road with the phone that lets you play games on Xbox LIVE and is embedded with 1400mAh battery. The browser includes Internet Explorer Mobile, Bing Search and Maps. The messaging features have Email, MMS, SMS, and Voice Mail.\r\n\r\nThe other important features in Dell Venue Pro are G-sensor, e-compass, proximity sensor, ambient light sensor, FM radio, GPS, micro USB I/O. the dimensions are 64.4x121.6x14.9 mm and weight 192 grams. Dell Venu Pro is known for its slick slide-down keyboard, fantastic build quality, and great performance. '),
